| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0069 — Recovery Inhibition (donutleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1fa2b395-bc5b-5dd2-b5ce-0ccf4cefcc5d"
